1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,360
Hello and welcome to this test video.

2
00:00:03,360 --> 00:00:07,440
This is a demonstration of the YouTube dubbing pipeline.

3
00:00:07,440 --> 00:00:11,840
The pipeline uses Faster Whisper for speech recognition

4
00:00:11,840 --> 00:00:15,920
and HTTS for text-to-speech synthesis.

5
00:00:15,920 --> 00:00:21,040
With Timeline Audio, the dub speech matches the original timing.

6
00:00:21,040 --> 00:00:23,840
Thank you for watching this demonstration.
